{"tid":802571,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得其實2012年世界末日其實係真 個世界根本一早已經毀滅左","createTime":"2018-09-01T14:12:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T14:22:12.000Z","uid":202560,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ffa480110f5722d74650b961649f7a8df92bdec2","tid":802571,"uid":202560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T14:12:59.000Z","msg":"唔知點解我覺得由2013年開始,明明自己身邊又好,成個世界又好,都發生左好多大事,但就係無咩印象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時候回憶翻依幾年,明明過左好多年,硬係覺得好似只過左幾個月咁,日日都好似重複咁,所有感受都好似唔係真實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2012年智能手機開始普及,然後社交媒體whatsapp果D又開始流行,香港個流行文化又慢慢被韓國影響,你見D女仔打扮完全唔同曬,感覺個世界變左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實可能瑪雅預言真係有根據,有無人同我一樣都有依種感覺?"},{"pid":"307825946e429281bd9eb00716f74bab7bda6d2a","tid":802571,"uid":29929,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T14:15:38.000Z","msg":"自己腦退化吹撚到世界末日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真荒謬 把自己看得那麼高"},{"pid":"82a240c4d427e094c206df1a5451d1c06fdf633d","tid":802571,"uid":205742,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T14:15:40.000Z","msg":"又好似係喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eda8273015887cbee60828ca3b27079ef2cdddf2","tid":802571,"uid":202560,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"307825946e429281bd9eb00716f74bab7bda6d2a","tid":802571,"uid":29929,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T14:15:38.000Z","msg":"自己腦退化吹撚到世界末日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真荒謬 把自己看得那麼高"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T14:17:28.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗咁講野啊 都係突然感觸姐 幾時有睇高自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45457d40542e5ec9fdffcfc135a0814b165a7071","tid":802571,"uid":3700,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,